CommandExecuter¶

robot.commands.CommandExecuter.CommandExecuter

class CommandExecuter(comque, statque, comreg, comevent, statevent)[source]¶

Bases: object

Enforces singleton object by creating an instance of this class. Only changes _instance once, that is, this class can only be instantiated once. Smaller number means higher priority.
